data.description: Built in 2022 Bliss Model, charming single-story! 3B/2B, 1,350 sq ft with a fully landscaped backyard including a custom pool with 12 x 9 Baja Deck great for entertaining! Seller completed private appraisal came in at $450,000.  This well-thought-out floorplan has a spacious great room, split primary room, and an open kitchen. The beautifully designed kitchen features recessed canned lighting, gas oven range, and beautiful backsplash, and an eat-in kitchen. The primary suite is split with an En-suite bathroom and walk-in closet! Premium lot strategic in having only single-story homes on each side for backyard pool privacy. Pentair pool pump allows owners to access remotely with Bluetooth.  Also Listed FOR RENT, MLS #6620269. PRESS MORE.. Owners also paid for builder upgrades such as Craftsman stone exterior, Coach lighting, Garage key pad, garage extension of 2' and raised interior height of garage 1', extra lot premium to be strategic in having only single-story homes on each side for backyard pool privacy. Wired to set up an accessory to change the Pool electronically too.  Outside has a covered patio and a spacious backyard,   this rare gem will go fast as not many homes have added pools yet around this area!
